## Route Configuration (Exact)

TanStack Router file-based routing conventions [web:79]:
- `index.tsx` в†’ `/`
- `subjects.tsx` в†’ `/subjects`
- `lesson.$slug.tsx` в†’ `/lesson/$slug`
- `about.tsx` в†’ `/about`
- `contact.tsx` в†’ `/contact`
- `login.tsx` в†’ `/login`
- `register.tsx` в†’ `/register`
- `(learner)/_layout.tsx` в†’ layout for `/subjects/intermediate`, `/subjects/advanced`, `/progress`
- `(learner)/subjects.intermediate.tsx` в†’ `/subjects/intermediate`
- `(learner)/subjects.advanced.tsx` в†’ `/subjects/advanced`
- `(learner)/progress.tsx` в†’ `/progress`
- `(admin)/_layout.tsx` в†’ layout for `/admin`, `/admin/content`
- `(admin)/admin.index.tsx` в†’ `/admin`
- `(admin)/admin.content.tsx` в†’ `/admin/content`

Route guards implemented via `beforeLoad` on layout routes.

## Access Control Matrix

| Route | Auth Required | Role | Behavior if Unauthenticated |
|-------|--------------|------|----------------------------|
| `/` | No | Any | Full access |
| `/subjects` | No | Any | Shows Beginner subjects only |
| `/lesson/:slug` | No for Beginner | Any | Public if level=awali, redirect to `/login` if level=kati/endelea |
| `/about` | No | Any | Full access |
| `/contact` | No | Any | Full access |
| `/login` | No (redirect if auth) | Any | Redirect to `/` if already logged in |
| `/register` | No (redirect if auth) | Any | Redirect to `/` if already logged in |
| `/subjects/intermediate` | Yes | learner, admin | Redirect to `/login?redirect=/subjects/intermediate` |
| `/subjects/advanced` | Yes | learner, admin | Redirect to `/login?redirect=/subjects/advanced` |
| `/progress` | Yes | learner, admin | Redirect to `/login?redirect=/progress` |
| `/admin` | Yes | admin only | Redirect to `/` if not admin |
| `/admin/content` | Yes | admin only | Redirect to `/` if not admin |

## Implementation Order (Strict вЂ” Do Not Skip)

1. **Project scaffolding** вЂ” `npm create vite@latest ahlusunna-web -- --template react-ts`, install all dependencies
2. **Configure TanStack Router** вЂ” add `@tanstack/router-plugin` to vite.config.ts, create `src/routes` directory
3. **Configure Tailwind** вЂ” create tailwind.config.js with exact color tokens, typography, spacing
4. **Configure TypeScript** вЂ” strict mode, path aliases for `@/components`, `@/contexts`, etc.
5. **Add Google Fonts** вЂ” import Inter, Amiri, Scheherazade New in index.css
6. **Create types** вЂ” `src/types/index.ts` with all interfaces
7. **Create mock data** вЂ” `src/data/seed.ts` with levels, subjects, 15 lessons, 3 users
8. **Configure i18n** вЂ” `src/i18n/config.ts` + `public/locales/sw.json`, `ar.json`, `en.json`
9. **Create utils** вЂ” `src/lib/utils.ts` with `cn()` helper
10. **Create contexts** вЂ” AuthContext, LanguageContext, AudioPlayerContext
11. **Create root layout** вЂ” `src/routes/__root.tsx` with Navbar + Outlet + PersistentAudioPlayer + Footer
12. **Create public routes** вЂ” index.tsx, subjects.tsx, lesson.$slug.tsx, about.tsx, contact.tsx
13. **Create auth routes** вЂ” login.tsx, register.tsx
14. **Create protected learner routes** вЂ” (learner)/_layout.tsx with beforeLoad guard, subjects.intermediate.tsx, subjects.advanced.tsx, progress.tsx
15. **Create admin routes** вЂ” (admin)/_layout.tsx with role guard, admin.index.tsx, admin.content.tsx
16. **Create all components** вЂ” in order: layout в†’ shared в†’ home в†’ subjects в†’ lesson в†’ auth в†’ audio в†’ admin
17. **Add progress tracking** вЂ” localStorage persistence for completed lessons
18. **Test all routes** вЂ” verify public access, auth guards, admin guards, RTL switching
19. **Polish responsive** вЂ” test at 320px, 768px, 1024px, 1280px
20. **Final accessibility audit** вЂ” keyboard navigation, focus states, aria labels

